<messages>

    <message id="whatis.menu">What is Trokam?</message>
    <message id="whatis.body">

        <div class="container">

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>What is Trokam?</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Trokam is a project aimed to develop a fair online search engine.</p>

            <p class="lead">Trokam respect your privacy, it does not track your preferences.</p>

            <p class="lead">Trokam search results are ad-free.</p>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>What does <em>Fair</em> Search Engine means?</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Fair Search Engine means that,</p>
           
            <ul>
                <li class="lead"><strong>Search results are auditable.</strong> The user could know why the web sites are listed in a particular order.</li>
                <li class="lead"><strong>Algorithms upon which is build are available as
                <a href="https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html" target="_blank">free software.</a></strong> The user is enbled to reproduce and analyse the same processing used by Trokam.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Could I use Trokam?</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Yes, on-going efforts are on developing <strong><a href="http://step2.trokam.com/">step2.trokam.com</a></strong>. <strong>Try it!</strong></p>

            <p class="lead">You could try the prototype in <strong><a href="http://step1.trokam.com/">step1.trokam.com</a></strong>. Its development is frozen.</p>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Who is developing Trokam?</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Trokam is been developed by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolasslusarenko" target="_blank">Nicolas Slusarenko</a> in his spare time, with
                            the help of a small but (hopefully!) enlarging community. <a href="http://project.trokam.com/proc/info/contact">Get in contact!</a></p>

            <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

            <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

        </div>
    </message>

    <message id="improve.menu">Improve Trokam</message>
    <message id="improve.body">

        <div class="container">

            <div class="jumbotron">

                <div>
                    <h1>Help to Improve Trokam</h1>
                </div>

                <p>There several ways you could help to improve Trokam.</p>

            </div>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Programming and Database Design</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Trokam runs on <a href="https://www.linuxfoundation.org/" target="_blank">GNU/Linux</a>, is programmed in
                            <a href="https://isocpp.org/" target="_blank">C++</a> and relies
                            on <a href="https://www.postgresql.org/" target="_blank">PostgreSQL</a> to store the data.</p>

            <p class="lead">You could browse <a href="https://github.com/trokam" target="_blank">all the code upon which Trokam is build</a>, because it is Free Software released as <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-2.0.html" target="_blank">GPLv2</a> or <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/quick-guide-gplv3.html" target="_blank">GPLv3</a>.</p>

            <p class="lead">Are you experienced on GNU/Linux, C++ programming, postgreSQL? Would you like to contribute? <a href="http://project.trokam.com/proc/info/contact">Get in contact!</a></p>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Translations</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Hopefully, Trokam would be useful to everyone on our planet.</p>

            <p class="lead">For that purpose we need to translate Trokam web site to every language nowadays in-use.</p>

            <p class="lead">Check the current translations, <a href="http://project.trokam.com/proc/info/contact">get in contact</a> and you might became one of the translators.</p>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Features and User Experience</h1>
            </div>

            <p class="lead">Trokam would be benefited from new ideas and user's feedback.</p>

            <p class="lead">Would you like that Trokam have a new feature? <a href="http://project.trokam.com/proc/info/contact">Happy to know about it!</a></p>

            <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

        </div>

    </message>

    <message id="whysponsor.menu">Why Sponsor Trokam?</message>
    <message id="whysponsor.body">

        <div class="container">

            <div class="row">
                
              <div class="col-md-4 alert alert-warning" role="alert">

                <div class="page-header">
                    <h1>Trokam's Social Contract</h1>
                </div>

                <p><strong>Trokam is an information service on the Internet.</strong> It analyses openly
                           available information on the Internet, process it and upon
                           request provides search results to users.</p>
                           
                <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

                <p><strong>Trokam is a Fair Search Engine,</strong> which implies that,
                
                    <ul style="list-style-type:circle">
                        <li><strong>Search results are auditable.</strong>
                            The user could know why the web sites are listed in a particular order.</li>
                        <li><strong>Algorithms upon which is build are available as
                            <a href="https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html" target="_blank">free software.</a></strong> 
                            The user is enbled to reproduce and analyse the same processing done by Trokam.</li>
                    </ul>                                       

                </p>

                <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

                <p><strong>Trokam runs entirely on the cloud.</strong> Trokam or Trokam's developers
                           will not buy hardware nor build any premisses.</p>
                
                <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>
                
                <p><strong>Trokam will no mix nor display advertisement with search results.</strong>
                           The results does not have any commercial bias.
                           Trokam does not sale any service nor any product. </p>
               
                <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>
               
                <p><strong>Trokam does not track your references.</strong>
                           Trokam does not bias the results with hidden information taken from you.</p>

                <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

                <p><strong>Trokam does not store nor publish what is been searched.</strong>
                           Trokam respect your privacy.</p>

                <hr/>

                <div class="page-header">
                    <p>
                        <strong>
                            Do you have any comment on this Social Contract?
                            <a href="http://project.trokam.com/proc/info/contact">Happy to know about it!</a>
                        </strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
              
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-8">

                <div class="page-header">
                    <h1>Why Sponsor Trokam?</h1>
                </div>

                <p class="lead">Do you think is worth an ad-free search engine?</p>

                <p class="lead">Do you like auditable results? Do you care about privacy?</p>

                <p class="lead">If you agree, <strong>you might consider sponsor Trokam with U$5 a year.</strong></p>

                <p class="lead">Trokam rely exclusively on sponsorships. When you became a sponsor, Trokam
                                commits with you to fulfill its Social Contract.</p>
                                
              </div>
              
            </div>

            <p>&nbsp;<br/></p>

